  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK758">
<l>kuṉṟēṟi yāṉaippōr kaṇṭaṟṟāṟ ṟaṉkaittoṉ</l>
<l>ṟuṇṭākac ceyvāṉ viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>An undertaking of one who has wealth in one's hands is like viewing an elephant-fight from a hill-top.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
